name: User tries to attempt actions on the Help Section from outside US
description: User tries to attempt actions on the Help Section from outside US
descriptionHtml: User tries to attempt actions on the Help Section from outside US

testStage.description: User tries to attempt actions on the Help Section from outside US

steps.name: I skip enrolling for easy pay card
I mock the location of the device to "CORNWALL_800786"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "CORNWALL_800786" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "CORNWALL_800786" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I click on "CHANGE STORE" button
I check that the "Want to change store?" pane is displayed
I click on "USE CURRENT LOCATION" button
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "HELP" tab
I get the text from the middle text area Outside US
I check that the application text: "CALL US ON: +1 855 276 1947" is equals to expected value: "CALL US ON: +1 855 276 1947"
